815
00:43:12,328 --> 00:43:14,330
including marrying you...

816
00:43:15,831 --> 00:43:16,832
Is a waste?

817
00:43:19,835 --> 00:43:22,337
Go back to the stacks, Daniel.

818
00:43:23,339 --> 00:43:26,841
The world needs
another graduate student.

