01:18:22,844 --> 01:18:24,812
Out of millions.

1422
01:18:28,250 --> 01:18:30,251
Well, if you're the FBI

1423
01:18:30,252 --> 01:18:33,821
and you know you
have to bring in something,

1424
01:18:33,822 --> 01:18:35,589
