Schmidt, 1942,

1479
01:20:39,700 --> 01:20:42,201
the political
affiliation of the defendant

1480
01:20:42,202 --> 01:20:43,903
was admitted as
establishing motive.

1481
01:20:43,904 --> 01:20:46,405
