if no crime was committed?

1544
01:23:14,488 --> 01:23:15,988
Why indeed?

1545
01:23:15,989 --> 01:23:18,991
I don't know how well
you remember Selig Mindish.

1546
01:23:18,992 --> 01:23:20,493
An ignorant man,

1547
01:23:20,494 --> 01:23:21,994
